This repository presents a detailed case study on Pepsi’s Sting strategy that challenged Red Bull’s dominance in India’s energy drink market. 
Red Bull built the market with premium pricing and aspirational branding, but Sting disrupted it by halving the price, introducing smaller packs, and leveraging Pepsi’s vast distribution network. 
The study includes a long-form analysis (CaseStudy.md), a summary (Summary.md), and key strategic insights (Insights.md) highlighting lessons on pricing, accessibility, localization, and distribution. 
A must-read for business analysts, marketers, and strategy enthusiasts.
